Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.81,0:00:51.48,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Laughters above
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.53,0:00:54.11,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Playful smiles
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.15,0:00:56.70,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Die get rolled
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.78,0:00:59.07,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Bathe in sorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:03.00,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}My tomorrow is built upon your flesh
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.04,0:01:04.58,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Slay the last of your kind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.66,0:01:12.59,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}To reclaim what's rightfully mine
