Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.75,0:01:10.04,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs-1\pos(640,673)}First time to make this
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.17,0:01:12.67,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs-1\pos(640,673)}Final dungeon 無念な未来の
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.75,0:01:14.01,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I have a reason
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:15.30,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Don't part the rivers
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.42,0:01:18.01,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Surround them, off with their heads
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:19.30,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Christen my motive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.34,0:01:20.60,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}First time to notice
